==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ti-]]'' (demonstrative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-al]]'' (correlative suffix of reason)

===Correlative===
'''tial'''

# for [[that]] reason (demonstrative correlative of reason)
#: As with other demonstrative correlatives in Esperanto, ''[[tial]]'' can be combined with ''[[ĉi]]'', the adverbial particle of proximity, or with ''[[for]]'', the adverbial particle of distance. ''Tial ĉi'' thus means ''for this reason [which I am indicating]'' and ''tial for'' means ''for that reason [as indicated by someone else]''.

